去指認他人
to point the finger.

35
00:01:01,130 --> 00:01:02,680
張嘴吧
Open your mouth.

36
00:01:05,950 --> 00:01:08,270
我知道你是什么東西
I know what you are.

37
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:18,250
讓他們進房間里去干  好嗎
Get 'em into a room, will ya?

38
00:01:18,860 --> 00:01:20,200
我馬上就回來
I'll be back in two shakes.

39
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,100
你要去哪
You're leaving?

40
