Are we certain we can trust her?

58
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:36,260
{\pos(188.308,233.999)}我們別無選擇

59
00:03:37,250 --> 00:03:39,900
我不確定這個仆人是否忠心
I'm not so sure the servant is loyal.

60
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:43,640
我曾經覺得你的倔強是個優點
I used to think your stubbornness a virtue.

61
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,090
你現在不覺得了嗎
And you don't any longer?

62
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:48,960
現在外面風聲鶴唳  你為何還要只身前往呢
Why go alone when there is influence in numbers?

63
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,670
那姑娘知道真相了
The girl has shown her color.

64
00:03:50,690 --> 00:03:52,850
但還不至于威脅到我們
We are well beyond the point of intimidation.

65
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:55,440
也許我們已經有被鏟除的危險了呢
Then perhaps we are at the point of elimination.

66
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,760
或許吧  但只是暫時的
Perhaps, but for the time being,

67
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:01,500
她活著遠比死了有價值
She is worth much more to us alive than dead.

68
