*寧入地獄*
*Better pray for hell*

74
00:04:27,670 --> 00:04:33,750
*不留人間*
*Not hallelujah*

75
00:04:57,590 --> 00:05:00,170
看看誰來了 梅西  西布里夫人
Look who's here, Mercy. Mrs.Sibley.

76
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:02,600
-坐起來  -你先出去吧
-Sit up straight, girl. - Leave us.

77
00:05:03,410 --> 00:05:04,990
你先出去  牧師
Leave us, reverend.

78
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,010
好的
Yes.

79
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,040
遵命
Certainly.

80
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:17,330
你昨晚來找過我
You came to visit me last night.

81
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:18,860
有嗎
Did I?

82
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:21,510
不用再裝了
The time for coyness has passed.

83
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:26,920
很明顯  你很清楚我的身份
It is clear you know exactly who and what I am.

84
00:05:27,990 --> 00:05:30,060
唯一的問題是
The only question that remains

85
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,410
你會怎么做
is what you will do with that information.

86
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,200
那取決于你  西布里夫人
That depends on you, Mrs. Sibley.

87
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,710
你想怎樣  小姑娘
What do you want, girl?

88
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:45,180
我想要你停止
I want it to stop...

89
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:50,490
那些痛苦與折磨
the torture, the torment, the suffering.

90
00:05:52,490 --> 00:05:54,050
否則我就會說出去
Or I will tell them.

91
00:05:54,170 --> 00:05:57,580
我會告訴大家你的真實身份
I will tell them all who and what you are.

92
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,000
你根本對我一無所知
You know nothing of me...

93
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:05,070
你不知道我做了什么  放棄了什么
or what I've done or given up

94
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,650
經歷了什么才變成今天的樣子
or endured to be who I am.

95
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:12,580
你受刑是因為你反抗
You are tortured because you resist.

96
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:18,150
屈服于我  你就會體驗到其中的樂趣
Give in to me, and you will know only pleasure.

97
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:19,910
你折磨我
You torture me.

98
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:24,410
你把那條蛇放進了我身體里
You put the snake inside of me.

99
00:06:24,410 --> 00:06:26,670
你就是那個咬我肩膀的女巫
You are the hag that bites my shoulder.

100
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:29,410
說話小心點  否則你的愚蠢
Careful, or your foolishness

101
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:32,390
會讓你的價值相形見絀
will come to overshadow your usefulness.

102
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:35,600
你之所以還活著
You live still...

103
00:06:37,050 --> 00:06:38,530
是因為我允許你活著
because I allow it.

104
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:42,500
你還能呼吸是因為我想讓你呼吸
You breathe only because I wish it.

105
00:06:44,470 --> 00:06:45,790
你會殺我嗎
You would kill me?

106
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,700
如果你亂說的話
If you speak.

107
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:53,560
保持沉默  你就能活下去
Stay silent, and you shall live.

108
00:06:58,820 --> 00:07:02,010
我深不可測  內心豐盈
My heart is deep and full.

109
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:06,820
我很想再給你一次機會讓你證明自己的價值
It yearns to give you further chance to prove your worth.

110
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:10,870
讓我失望  就是讓你自己失望
Fail me, and you fail yourself.

111
00:07:14,450 --> 00:07:16,360
拋尸山壑等待你的最終決定
The crag awaits your decision.

112
00:07:45,670 --> 00:07:46,590
該死
Damn it.

113
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:13,670
你找我嗎
You sent for me?

114
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,380
對
Yes.

115
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,310
如果你想再次羞辱我
If your purpose is further humiliation

116
00:09:19,310 --> 00:09:20,710
或想繼續探尋心靈
or probings of the heart,

117
00:09:21,110 --> 00:09:22,870
我已經受夠了
I, for one, have had my fill.

118
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,740
我想給你個建議
My purpose is a proposition.

119
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:31,470
其實是想跟你做筆買賣
A business arrangement of sorts.

120
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:32,830
你說
I'm listening.

121
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:36,060
你告訴我
In which you would tell me

122
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:38,280
你一周最多能賺多少錢
the sum of your most fruitful week's bounty,

123
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:43,170
我永久性地給你雙倍的錢
and I shall provide double in perpetuity...

124
00:09:44,930 --> 00:09:46,030
你來陪我
for your company...

125
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:49,680
把你寶貴的時間給我
and your precious time...

126
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,650
只給我一個人
in exclusivity.

127
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,870
你想徹底把我買下來
So you wish to buy me outright.

128
00:10:05,290 --> 00:10:06,400
我是家里的獨子
I'm an only child.

129
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:10,320
我不喜歡與人分享
I never learned to share.

130
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:14,150
你這是向我道歉嗎
Which is as close as a man like you comes to an apology.

131
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:19,050
你看到我跟其他人在一起
Was it really so very painful for you

132
00:10:19,050 --> 00:10:20,280
真的很痛苦嗎
to see me with another?

133
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:23,590
真的
Yes.

134
00:10:39,050 --> 00:10:40,230
你愿意成為我的人嗎
Will you be mine?

135
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:05,690
柯頓
Cotton.

136
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,780
奧登上尉
Captain Alden!

137
00:11:12,090 --> 00:11:13,250
你怎么來了
What brings you here?

138
00:11:20,930 --> 00:11:21,900
因為這個
This.

139
00:11:28,050 --> 00:11:28,930
你確定嗎  多蒂
Are you sure, Dottie?

140
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:30,820
你確定她不會傷害我們
Are you sure she won't hurt us?

141
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:32,460
她肯定不會傷害我們的...
'Course she won't hurt us...

142
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,830
除非你是個巫師
...unless you be a witch.

143
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,940
你好  梅西
Hello, Mercy.

144
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:50,650
我們可以進去嗎
May we come in?

145
00:12:05,570 --> 00:12:07,270
他們會到你屋里找你嗎  梅西
They come to you in your room, Mercy?

146
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:08,980
他們...
Them...

147
00:12:10,070 --> 00:12:10,980
巫師
witches?

148
00:12:13,300 --> 00:12:14,340
有時吧
Sometimes...

149
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:20,040
有時候會在其他地方
And other times in other places.

150
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,860
他們現在在這里嗎
Are they here with us now?

151
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,140
現在你能看到他們嗎
Can you see them as we speak?

152
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,990
不  他們現在不在
No, I don't see them now.

153
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:33,580
他們會傷害你嗎
Do they hurt you?

154
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,950
有時候會
Sometimes.

155
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,910
那是種什么感覺
What's it like?

156
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,880
什么什么感覺
What's it like?

157
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,960
伸手指認別人
To point your finger

158
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,660
讓別人膽戰心驚
and make them shake and tremble with fear.

159
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:48,000
指認別人  看著他們逃跑
To point your finger and watch them run.

160
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:52,160
不  不是那樣的
No, it's not like that...

161
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,950
根本不是
at all.

162
00:12:54,430 --> 00:12:55,410
我發誓
I swear.

163
00:12:55,730 --> 00:12:58,820
塞勒姆沒有哪個女人能有那種權力
No woman in Salem has ever had that kind of power.

164
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,750
連瑪麗·西布里都沒有
Not even Mary Sibley.

165
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:18,640
你們是說我...
You think I have sway...

166
00:13:21,190 --> 00:13:22,780
在塞勒姆民眾之中有支配力量
...amongst all the people of Salem?

167
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:27,020
你手指所向便關乎生死
Your little finger points to life a-and death itself.

168
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:30,880
告訴我們  巫師是什么樣子
Tell us... what do the witches look like?

169
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:38,990
還有件事  西布里夫人
One more thing, Mrs. Sibley...

170
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,310
碼頭有大量包裹
There was an overflow of parcels left on the britania,

171
00:13:41,310 --> 00:13:44,050
都應該交給一個叫威廉·霍克的人
all of which are to be delivered to a William Hooke.

172
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,320
我們四處都找遍了
Now, we've looked high and low.

173
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,860
但是沒人知道他的行蹤
No one could seem to locate the fellow.

174
00:13:47,450 --> 00:13:49,450
知道了  我會處理的
I see. I'll take care of it.

175
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:50,470
謝謝您  夫人
Thank you, madam.

176
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:55,040
他們不會找到霍克先生的  永遠不會
They will not find Mr. Hooke... not now, not ever.

177
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,610
我不會過問他的情況
I won't ask what happened to him.

178
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:57,600
你也不該過問
Nor should you.

179
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,680
那就保守秘密  免得有人起疑心
Then contain it before curiosity grows.

180
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:04,390
西布里夫人  下午好
Uh, Mrs. Sibley, uh, good afternoon.

181
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:06,610
能麻煩她跟我走一趟嗎
Might I borrow your girl?

182
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:10,760
我家夫人吃了有問題的貽貝  病得厲害
The missus has taken ill with a batch of wayward mussels

183
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:14,790
想要她特制的藥劑來一緩病痛
and now begs relief with one of her exceptional tonics.

184
00:14:15,850 --> 00:14:19,090
請向霍爾夫人致以我最迫切的問候
Please send Mrs. Hale my most urgent regrets.

185
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:20,720
您有心了
Most kind.

186
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:30,910
理查茲先生  請把這位霍克先生
Oh, Mr. Richards, uh, fetch for me a list of items

187
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,770
要收取的貨物清單給我一份
this Mr. Hooke was here to receive,

188
